# Poker ai player
## Description
This is a poker ai player that can play poker with other players. It is based on the [poker game](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poker). Unlimited players can join and play with unlimited ai instances
## How to run
### Prerequisites
- Python 3.6 or higher
- pip
- requirements.txt
### Installation
1. Clone the repository
2. Install the requirements
3. Run the server.py file
4. Run the client.py file (multiple times for multiple players)
### Usage
- The server will ask for the number of players and the number of ai players
- The ai will leark from your play
- You can make ai play agains each other and let them learn from each other